          We made our way towards the Lincoln Memorial.
  
  = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_3805'})
  
  .Content
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          It was far busier during the day and by daylight, we could see far more of the surrounding area.
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2688'})

