        :markdown
          We entered the large, cavernous monument.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2691'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_2698'], right: ['10/IMG_2699'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We returned down the steps from the memorial to the reflecting pool.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/DSC03592'})
