  .Content
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          From the World War II memorial, we then headed towards the Washington Monument.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2775'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/DSC03644'], right: ['10/DSC03653'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Unfortunately, the monument was closed for repairs after an earthquake in&nbsp;2012.

          We continued on, the White House looming into view in the distance.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2780'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2786'})
