      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After taking our photo outside of the Whitehouse, we continued on towards the Smithsonian museums.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_2799','10/DSC03699','10/IMG_3861'], right: ['10/IMG_2808','10/IMG_2810','10/IMG_2814','10/IMG_3862'] })
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/DSC03708'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We arrived at the Smithsonian National Air and Space Museum.

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_of_interest", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '10/DSC03717', title: 'National Air and Space Museum', address: '600 Independence Ave SW, Washington, DC 20560, USA', place: 'Museum', rating: 5, link:'' })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          The large, spacious foyer was filled with models of rockets, planes, and other aircrafts.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/DSC03728'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2826'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We explored the ground floor, replete with a replica of the Lunar Lander.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_3876','10/IMG_2836','10/IMG_2880'], right: ['10/IMG_3888','10/IMG_2838'] })
    
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We stopped for lunch at the food court. I grabbed a burger from McDonalds (it was unsurprisingly, very familiar).

          After lunch, we made our way up the second floor, to continue exploring the various displays.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2887'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_3899','10/IMG_3912'], right: ['10/IMG_3909'] })
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_2892'], right: ['10/IMG_2895'] })
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2905'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After exploring the second floor, and taking a look through the gift shop, we departed.
          
          Outside the museum, Butcher and I took the opportunity to try the Astronaut ice cream we’d picked up from the gift shop.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_3946'], right: ['10/IMG_3948'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          <em>“Like chalky ice cream”</em>

    = partial("photoessays/components/video", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, video: '10/IMG_3947'})

