          Eventually we arrived at our second museum for the day; the National Museum of Natural History.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_2932'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/place_of_interest", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '10/IMG_2802', title: 'National Museum of Natural History', address: '10th St. & Constitution Ave. NW, Washington, DC 20560, United States', place: 'Museum', rating: 5, link:'' })
  = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_3971'})
  .Content
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          This museum was equally impressive, with lifelike models of creatures from many different periods of time on Earth.

          We set about exploring the museum.
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_2934','10/IMG_2946','10/IMG_3001','10/IMG_4025'], right: ['10/IMG_3951','10/IMG_2996','10/IMG_3000','10/IMG_4032'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          The museum and its displays were very impressive.
          
          Unfortunately I was beginning to fade a little, and was unable to fully enjoy the latter half of our time there. All the running around of that day was starting to catch up to me.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_3009'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Later that afternoon, we departed the museum, heading for our hotel.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_3048'})      
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['10/IMG_3056'], right: ['10/IMG_3063'] })
    
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We arrived to find three police cars outside our hotel.

          We never learned why they were there. Just another day at the Allen Lee.
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_4041'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We caught out breath, and packed our bags for departure to New York the following day.

          ---

          Later that evening, we set off in search of food.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '10/IMG_4044'})
    
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We soon found an interesting Italian chain called Vapiano.

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_restaurant", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '10/vapiano', title: 'Vapiano', address: '1800 M St NW, Washington, DC 20036, USA', price: '$$', menu: 'Italian', rating: 4, link: '' })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          It had an interesting ordering system where you were given a card you’d swipe to order food, and then when you left, you paid the balance.
        
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: 'Some pretty good carbs', photo: '10/IMG_4047'}) 

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          I’m sure this was designed to try to take advantage of human psychology and encourage you to order more, and it nearly worked on me as I considered ordering some Tiramisu for dessert.

          After a pleasant dinner, we decided to turn in early, given our departure the next day. Our time in Washington was brief, and jam-packed.

