    .Row#august-11
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          ---

          The next morning, we checked out of the Allen Lee and made our way to the nearest underground station, luggage in tow.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '11/IMG_4051'}) 
